snippet: As his tee shot curled farther and farther away from the 17th fairway, heading toward all sorts of trouble, Tiger Woods simply stuffed his club in the bag....

headline.print_headline: Woods Shows His Rust on Rough Day at Hoylake
headline.main: Woods Shows His Rust on Rough Day at Hoylake

lead_paragraph: As his tee shot curled farther and farther away from the 17th fairway, heading toward all sorts of trouble, Tiger Woods simply stuffed his club in the bag.
